			<div class="article-correspondence layout-item fill-pattern-light">
		<div class="layout-item-intro">
			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="2062">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>I am more gullible than most, so I must write to ask if Poe Ballantine is actually dead. I have always enjoyed his work, and was particularly moved by his essay in the June issue, &ldquo;<a href="/article/634">Where the Rain Belongs</a>.&rdquo; His contributor&rsquo;s note in that issue says he drowned while crossing the Atlantic in a canoe. Please let me know whether this is true. As I said, I am extremely gullible &mdash; or, actually, I hope I am extremely gullible.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Margie Gowen<br>Address Withheld</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

								<div class="block-correspondence-respond fill-pattern-light" id="2063">
								<p><a href="/contributors/poe-ballantine"><strong>Poe Ballantine</strong></a> responds:</p>
							<p>Every now and then it&rsquo;s kind of hard to tell, but, yes, I&rsquo;m still alive. I don&rsquo;t even know how to canoe. Bless everyone for their concern, cards, letters, flowers, and M&amp;M&rsquo;s.</p>
	</div>


					</div>

				<div class="text-center">
			<button class="b b-1 xsmall js-b-readmore-correspondence" data-collapsible="#article-correspondences" data-label="Read More Letters">Read More Letters</button>
		</div>
			</div>
    
		<div class="article-correspondence-cta">
		<div class="cta cta-l1" data-url="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">
			<div class="cta-intro">
				<h5 class="cta-title alt-ff">Thinking about writing us a letter?</h5>
				<p class="cta-text">Give in to the temptation. We love getting mail. <br><span class="xsmall">(Of course, we reserve the right to edit.)</span></p>
